sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/GitOps
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant DSCCtrl as DataScienceCluster Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant GitHub as GitHub Manifest Repos<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Metrics as Metrics Endpoint<br/>8443/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Metrics: Flow 1: Component Deployment via DataScienceCluster

    User->>K8sAPI: Create DataScienceCluster CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Watch notification<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    DSCCtrl->>GitHub: Fetch component manifests<br/>HTTPS (public repos)
    GitHub-->>DSCCtrl: Manifest tarballs

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply Kustomize manifests<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Resource creation confirmation

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update DSC status<br/>Component versions
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR status updated

    Note over User,Metrics: Flow 2: Monitoring Metrics Collection

    Prom->>Metrics: GET /metrics<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Metrics-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics (text)

    Prom->>K8sAPI: Scrape component metrics<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Prom: Metrics data

    Note over User,Metrics: Flow 3: Platform Initialization via DSCInitialization

    User->>K8sAPI: Create DSCInitialization CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Watch notification

    activate DSCCtrl
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create namespaces<br/>redhat-ods-applications<br/>redhat-ods-monitoring
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Configure Service Mesh<br/>ServiceMeshMember resources
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Deploy Prometheus/Alertmanager<br/>Monitoring stack
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Configure trusted CA bundle<br/>ConfigMaps
    deactivate DSCCtrl

    K8sAPI-->>User: Platform initialized

    Note over User,Metrics: Flow 4: OAuth Client Generation

    activate DSCCtrl
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Get component Route<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Route hostname

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create OAuthClient<br/>redirect_uri from Route
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: OAuth client created

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Secret<br/>{component}-oauth-client-secret
    deactivate DSCCtrl
    K8sAPI-->>User: OAuth client ready
